Package: formiko
Version: 1.3.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Ondřej Tůma <mcbig@zeropage.cz>
Installed-Size: 276
Depends: gir1.2-gtksource-3.0, gir1.2-gtkspell3-3.0, gir1.2-webkit2-4.0, python3-docutils, python3-gi, python3-recommonmark, python3:any (>= 3.3.2-2~)
Suggests: vim-gtk3
Section: editors
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/ondratu/formiko
Description: reStructuredText and MarkDown editor and live previewer
 Features:
  * GtkSourceView based editor with syntax highlighting
  * possible use Vim editor
  * vertical or horizontal window splitting
  * preview mode
  * periodic save file
  * json and html preview
